snippet.textDisplay: Hey Brad! I love your videos and i was hoping for some advice. I'm going to volunteer in Nepal for six months, and i am panicking about what to do with my hair! I'm super insecure about my hair at the moment, whenever i went abroad before I always had waist length mermaid hair which looked cute unstyled but now i have it short and it just looks like a hedge! snippet.textDisplay: Let’s take a trip down memory lane. I had waist length hair. It was the day before the Valentine’s Day dance in 8th grade. It was 2am and I was curling my hair bc I wouldn’t have time for it in the morning. Suddenly I had a panic attack and chopped my hair to my shoulders. It looked surprisingly good but I still ran to my moms room 2:30 am crying with my hair in my hands. She didn’t yell at me just hugged me while I cried and said it looked cute.
